headline: Workday Announces Annual Stockholder Meeting
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), the AI platform for managing people and money, today announced that its 2025 annual meeting of stockholders will be held virtually on Wednesday, June 4, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. Pacific Time / 12:00 p.m. Eastern Time.
